import React from 'react'
import {useState} from 'react'
import {Modal, ModalHeader, ModalTitle, Form, Button} from 'react-bootstrap'

const AddClubModel = ({handleShow, handleClose, show}) => {
  return (
    <>
      <Button variant='primary' onClick={handleShow}>
        Add Club
      </Button>

      <Modal show={show} onHide={handleClose}>
        <Modal.Header closeButton>
          <Modal.Title>Add Club</Modal.Title>
        </Modal.Header>
        <Modal.Body>
          <Form>
            <Form.Group className='mb-3' controlId='exampleForm.ControlInput1'>
              <Form.Label>Club</Form.Label>
              <Form.Control
                className='mb-2'
                type='text'
                placeholder='Club'
                autoFocus
              />
              <Form.Label>Brand</Form.Label>
              <Form.Control type='text' placeholder='Brand' autoFocus />
            </Form.Group>
          </Form>
        </Modal.Body>
        <Modal.Footer>
          <Button variant='secondary' onClick={handleClose}>
            Close
          </Button>
          <Button variant='primary' onClick={handleClose}>
            Save Changes
          </Button>
        </Modal.Footer>
      </Modal>
    </>
  )
}

export default AddClubModel
